#1400
Before a Gate in the Dunes~
  A wall of scrap metal stands to the south.  Large squares of random
pieces of metal make up the wall, making it look quite strange.  Some
of the squares are coated in rust, making it look as though some areas
would be less protected than others.  On top of the wall the silhouette
of a sentry silently paces back and forth.  In the middle of the wall
a gate stands as a way through.  To the north the path leads out back 
into the dunes.
